answer: well to me, all this "God" stuff doesn't make sense to me. the world couldn't be created in 7 days, you can't be brought back to live if you died (meaning you don't have a pulse and you're not breathing), you can't have 'supernatural' abilities and etc. I know i was jewish for most of my life and I always had my doubts. I don't know, I just think that religion at times is morally wrong in some aspects. I'm not saying that your religion is wrong. I believe that you should believe in what you want, if you're Christian, Jewish, a Buddhist, an Atheist and etc. so yes, I'm an atheist and I believe in nothing. the only thing I trust and believe in is science.
